{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"identifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which it is added."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"configurationURL","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An initialized raster tile source."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"},{"text":" documentation for more information about tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"majo